      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 9:6",
      "source_id": "asv",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-asv/PSA009.htm",
      "text": "The enemy are come to an end, they are desolate for ever; And the cities which thou hast overthrown, The very remembrance of them is perished.",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 9:6",
